data.description: Honey Stop The Car We Just Found Our Dream Home!! This beautiful, like new 4-bedroom 3 full bath home is located in The Groves. Upon entering the home, through the glass French Doors is a spacious office/study. The bright and airy kitchen is open to overlook the island and dining area. Enjoy your evenings in the living room by the gas fireplace. The primary suite is located downstairs in the rear of the home. The HUGE primary bathroom is perfect for those with a large wardrobe. It has not one, but two oversized walk-in closets. There is an additional bedroom downstairs along with a full bathroom. Upstairs you will find an open game room that leads to two bedrooms and the third full bathroom. The backyard has an oversized covered patio with enough space for all of your gatherings. ( Appliances not included)
